From cou.: 165 H 0(1,1) = 2.1486, H0(2,2) = 5.1589, H0(3,3) = 6.0121, H0(4,4) = 6.0313, H0(5,5) = 6.0542, H0(6,6) = 8.7463, H0(7,7) = 9.9811, H0(8,8) = 12.9747.
